Incredible Connection’s Festive Gift Guide is now live, with discounts on a wide range of technology products available. The specials in the gift guide are available from 2-24 December 2020. All items listed are available to purchase online from the Incredible Connection website, while a wide range of the deals are also available in-store. Professional and gaming laptops, PlayStation consoles, smartwatches and smartphones, printers, keyboards and mice, headphones, sound systems, hard drives, TVs, cameras, and more are on offer at reduced prices. A selection of the deals available from Incredible Connection are shown below. You can see all the deals on offer on the Incredible Connection website. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-378744" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/DSLR-Bundle.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/DSLR-Bundle.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/DSLR-Bundle-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/DSLR-Bundle-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-378746" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Galaxy-A21s.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Galaxy-A21s.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Galaxy-A21s-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Galaxy-A21s-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-378748" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Razer-Blade.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-c